Text: 'The Government of Karnataka is going to give Bangalore its very own New York-style
  Times Square very soon. The mayor of the city, R Sampath Raj, stated that this grand
  landmark will be at one of the most popular spots of Bangalore: the intersection
  at Residency Road and Brigade Road in the central business district.


  The proposed Bangalore Square will be a hub of entertainment, business, and commercial
  centers, and it is also expected to come up on a massive 25 acres of land. Stating
  that Bangalore is rapidly becoming a global city, the city mayor said the Bangalore  everything
  I saw I enjoyed alot unforgettable memory.'
